            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<h2> </h2>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-61-pixels\">\n<p><strong>Week</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-76-pixels\">\n<p><strong>Datum</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-378-pixels\">\n<p><strong>Opdracht</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-170-pixels\">\n<p><strong>Deadline</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-61-pixels\">\n<p>1</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-76-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-378-pixels\">\n<p>Inleiding, planning, groepsindeling, start ori\u00ebntatie</p>\n<p>Padlet om voorkennis te activeren</p>\n<p>Uitleg over ICT middelen en mogelijkheden in het (basis) onderwijs. </p>\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-170-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-61-pixels\">\n<p>2</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-76-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-378-pixels\">\n<p>Ori\u00ebntatie, planning uitvoering</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-170-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-61-pixels\">\n<p>3</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-76-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-378-pixels\">\n<p>Ori\u00ebntatie</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-170-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-61-pixels\">\n<p>4</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-76-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-378-pixels\">\n<p>Ori\u00ebntatie/ ontwerp</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-170-pixels\">\n<p>Product ori\u00ebntatie</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-61-pixels\">\n<p>5</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-76-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-378-pixels\">\n<p>Ontwerp</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-170-pixels\">\n<p>Product ontwerp</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-61-pixels\">\n<p>6</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-76-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-378-pixels\">\n<p>Uitvoering</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-170-pixels\">\n<p>Product uitvoering</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-61-pixels\">\n<p>7</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-76-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-378-pixels\">\n<p>Uitvoering</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-170-pixels\">\n<p>Product uitvoering</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-61-pixels\">\n<p>8</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-76-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-378-pixels\">\n<p>Evaluatie</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-170-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"width-61-pixels\">\n<p>9</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-76-pixels\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-378-pixels\">\n<p>Evaluatie</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"width-170-pixels\">\n<p>Product evaluatie</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n"
