            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<h2>Ondersteunende informatie:</h2>\n<p><strong>Theorie:</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://npcg.sharepoint.com/:w:/s/np-teampw-oa/EdkK3Qkf5UNKmJkJRgXiEi4BoHz7J7aj6iFmsCu3JU6mvw?e=qet5rK\"><span class=\"underline\">10 pijlers van digitale didactiek</span></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/file:///C:/Users/i.appeldorn/OneDrive%20-%20Noorderpoort/2018-2019/Onderwijs%20ontwikkeling/Digitale%20didactiek/Whitepaper_21st_Century_Skills_in_het_onderwijs.pdf\"><span class=\"underline\">21e eeuwse vaardigheden</span></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/file:///C:/Users/i.appeldorn/OneDrive%20-%20Noorderpoort/2018-2019/Onderwijs%20ontwikkeling/Digitale%20didactiek/Wat%20is%20gepersonaliseerd%20onderwijs.docx\"><span class=\"underline\">Wat is gepersonaliseerd onderwijs</span></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://leerling2020.nl/wp-content/uploads/resultaten-uploads/2016/05/Motivatie-tools.pdf\"><span class=\"underline\">Digitale tools inzetten om leerlingen te motiveren</span></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://npcg-my.sharepoint.com/:w:/g/personal/i_appeldorn_noorderpoort_nl/ER2G0gZBRElGnlPfqh3NvlQB9PuhokBCqC0RjOGyRsZz1A?e=xuuozb\"><span class=\"underline\">Handleiding PowToon Nederlands</span></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://leerling2020.nl/flipping-the-classroom-voor-beginners/\"><span class=\"underline\">Flipping the classroom voor beginners</span></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Methodes &amp; tools:</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://leerling2020.nl/productreviews/\"><span class=\"underline\">Reviews apps en tools door docenten</span></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://npcg.sharepoint.com/:x:/s/np-teampw-oa/EbYjvn5W8elGmoxJc3ntrRkBDypWF4R1MpdvkU9k9Ry6gw?e=QJO9hW\"><span class=\"underline\">Schema inzet digitale didactiek</span></a></p>\n<p>Tijdschrift <a href=\"https://www.jilster.nl/\"><span class=\"underline\">https://www.jilster.nl/</span></a> (Nederlands)</p>\n<p>Infographic <a href=\"https://piktochart.com/formats/infographics/\"><span class=\"underline\">https://piktochart.com/formats/infographics/</span></a> (Engels)</p>\n<p>Animatie filmpje <a href=\"https://www.powtoon.com/\"><span class=\"underline\">https://www.powtoon.com</span></a> (Engels)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://basisonderwijs.online/digibordtools/html5/groepjesmaker.html\"><span class=\"underline\">Groepjesmaker</span></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Filmpjes &amp; animaties:</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=21ubM-j0ZNI\"><span class=\"underline\">filmpje 21e eeuwse vaardigheden 1</span></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nExpvLXap1U\"><span class=\"underline\">Filmpje gepersonaliseerd leren</span></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iQWvc6qhTds&amp;index=2&amp;list=PLveaPoz6DYAFAlcY4I5wLIcyG2_Qzr7bl\"><span class=\"underline\">Flipping the classroom</span></a> (Engels)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.kennisnet.nl/fileadmin/kennisnet/leren_ict/flipping_the_classroom/bijlagen/Infographic_Flipping_the_Classroom.pdf\"><span class=\"underline\">Infographic flipping the classroom</span></a> (Nederlands, Kennisnet)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xpjbtOU6lns\"><span class=\"underline\">School van de toekomst</span></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Programma's maken ICT portfolio:</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wix.com/\"><span class=\"underline\">https://www.wix.com</span></a> (Engels)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://sway.office.com/my\"><span class=\"underline\">https://sway.office.com/my</span></a> (Nederlands via Noorderportal)</p>\n<p>Google Sites: <a href=\"https://www.webwijzer.nl/pdf/google-sites.pdf\"><span class=\"underline\">Google Sites handleiding</span></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.wikiwijs.nl/\"><span class=\"underline\">Wikiwijs</span></a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Evaluatie mogelijkheden</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.reflectietoolbox.nl/\"><span class=\"underline\">http://www.reflectietoolbox.nl/</span></a></p>\n"
